cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a signature verification method using texture features extracted from signature images. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) as it involves image processing and feature extraction. The use of support vector machines (SVMs) for classification suggests that the paper may also fall under machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves statistical analysis, which could place it under information retrieval (cs.IR) or cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, the use of multiple datasets and comparison with existing systems suggests that the paper may also fall under multimedia (cs.MM).
